<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣- ما أُلْحِقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فِعلِل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(زِبْرِج)</span> :<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(فِعْلِم)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(دِلْقِم)</span> وهي الهَرِمَةُ من النُّوق.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤- ما أُلحقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلَلٍ)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(ضِفْدَعٍ)</span> :<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(فِعْوَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(خِرْوَعٍ)</span> وهو نوع من النّبات.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>و <span class="c2">(فِعْلَى)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(مِعْزَى)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥- ما أُلحقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فُعْلَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جُؤْذَرٍ)</span> وهو ما أثبته الكوفيّون:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(فُعْلَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(سُؤْدَدٍ)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ب-<span class="c5"> الملحقُ بالخُماسيِّ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(فَعَلْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(صَمَحْمَحٍ)</span> أُلحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَلّلِ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(سَفَرْجَلٍ)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(فَعَوْعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(عَثَوْثَلٍ)</span> وهو الكثير اللّحم ألحق –أيضاً- بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَلّلٍ)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(فَعَلَّى)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(حَبَنطًى)</span> وهو –أيضاً- ملحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَلَّل)</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(إِفْعَلّ)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(إِرْدَبٍّ)</span> ألحقَ بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلَلٍّ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(جِرْدَحْلٍ)</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(إِنْفَعَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(إِنْقَحْلٍ)</span> أحلقَ –أيضاً- بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلَلٍّ)</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(نَفْوَعِل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(نَخْوَرِشٍ)</span> للجَرْوِ إذا تحرّك فَخَدَشَ؛ وهو ملحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعْلَلِلٍ)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جَحْمَرِشٍ)</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(فعنعل)</span> نحو: <span class="c2">(عَقَنْقَل)</span> و <span class="c2">(عَصَنْصَر)</span> ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَلَّل)</span> .<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>